Class TensorIsCloseTo<S>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:
    S - the s
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.hamcrest.Matcher<Tensor<S>>, org.hamcrest.SelfDescribing

    public class TensorIsCloseTo<S>
extends org.hamcrest.TypeSafeDiagnosingMatcher<Tensor<S>>
    A hamcrest matcher for unit tests, that matches a values of a tensor to be within a certain tolerance compared to the values of a reference (expected) tensor. Further, the shapes of the two tensors have to be equal (conform with the Shape.equals(Object) method).
    See Also:
    org.tensorics.core.tensor.Shape, Field
